viewData.name: PhiLashes Adhesive Sticker
viewData.short_description: The PhiLashes Adhesive Sticker is used to cover the crystal stone so that the adhesive does not spread on the surface and it remains clean.
viewData.long_description: The PhiLashes Adhesive Sticker is used to cover the crystal stone so that the adhesive does not spread on the surface and it remains clean. This makes the eyelash lengthening much more efficient because it is easy to act, and also saves the preparation time.
